{"tid":582487,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哈化粉球場當眾手淫被捕","createTime":"2018-03-06T08:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T10:47:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1812848318160579d262a244a55858a172f5506b","tid":582487,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=7Q2v0T3c8BHQ%2B9PZjLsvqxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=6e69553b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】1名20來歲的的哈化柏林球迷，周末入場欣賞愛隊作客史浩克04的德甲聯賽，竟在看台當眾手淫，最終被當地警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter近日瘋傳一名哈化柏林粉絲，一邊現場看球賽一邊手淫的照片。該名貼圖的史浩克04球迷留言表示：「這種情景昨日（周六）真的在球場內發生，令人難以置信。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指，那位坐在史浩克04球場作客球迷區的哈化柏林粉絲，比賽期間半躺在座位上，突然脫下褲子，並伸手到私處有所動作。據悉，該名男子公然手淫不久，便被多位現場保安上前圍攏制止，並將他趕離球場，手淫男及後被當地警方拘捕，並落案控以猥褻等2條罪名。<br />\n<br />\n哈化柏林歇冬後於8場德甲只嘗1勝，並暫列積分榜第12位，球隊於上周六亦以0:1敗走史浩克04，莫非這就是涉事球迷因不滿而當眾「發洩」的理由？"},{"pid":"c6eee6639fc63f2afad91598db5f1f3fccdb8c6d","tid":582487,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"邊位波台ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a233149ff9aac50aaf43ff01cdbb3ec2cf7bf4a","tid":582487,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32023c2e8d419f63ba5a91ee6e1e9978fa5867aa","tid":582487,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"東德狗就係柒下柒下，唔似我地西德人咁有文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d81bdd254b7dda890bb26ac76f183262e8c727","tid":582487,"uid":23433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"輸波都要幫自己隊球隊打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s